query:
SELECT f.id, f.title, f.type, f.sessionNum, f.rating, 
       ur.name as revisor, ut.name as taquigrafo
FROM feedbacks f
INNER JOIN users ur ON f.revisorId = ur.id
INNER JOIN users ut ON f.taquigId = ut.id
ORDER BY f.id DESC
LIMIT 10
